            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Add the <strong>sliced garlic</strong> and<strong> sun-dried tomatoes</strong> to the pan and cook for 2-3 min</p><p>Add your <strong>flaked almonds</strong> to a baking tray and put the tray under the grill for 2-4 min or until toasted and lightly golden</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don't burn!</p>",
      "order": 4,
