    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, wash your <strong>spinach</strong>, then add to a colander and pour <strong>boiled water</strong> all over it so that it starts to wilt</p><p>Rinse the <strong>wilted spinach</strong> under <strong>cold running water</strong> until it's cool</p><p>Once cool, squeeze as much water out of the spinach as you can, then chop it roughly</p>",
