      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>Chinese rice wine</strong>, <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>and 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[195ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[250ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> to the pan with the sun-dried tomatoes and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>",
